name: News & Media TV Broadcaster Logos
description:
I needed some news logos for a job I was working on. I looked on the community for such a file to no avail so thought I'd share.


There are Original, Dark and White versions of most logos, use as you see fit. Note these might not follow as per their brand guidelines exactly in terms of colours but created the options anyway as good for 'as seen on' web carousels etc.
